We are presenting our project crazy taxi.
Team id: 457
For this project we have to install simplecpp code blocks 
Installation process :
 1)google search on simple codeblocks iitb.
2)go to simplecpp and click on install full version then code blocks will be installed on your pc
In code blocks create a new file and save it as .cpp format 
In game first we have created a init canvas
And we have made some rectangles as obstacles.
 we have defined functions like LEFT,RIGHT,FORWARD  to move the main rectangle . and we filled it with colours by simplecpp  graphics. 

